{"word":"G3004 - λέγω - légō - leg'-o - Ask","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">λέγω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>légō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>leg'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Ask"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சொல், பிரசங்கம் பண்ணு, உரை, கூப்பிடு, கட்டளையிடு, உபதேசம் பண்ணு, விசாரி, பரியாசம் பண்ணு, பாராட்டு, விளம்பு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to speak"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primary verb; properly to &ldquo;lay&rdquo; forth, that is, (figuratively) <i>relate</i> (in words [usually of systematic or set <i>discourse</i>; whereas <a href=\"#/G2036 - ἔπω - épō - ep'-o/2036\">G2036</a> and <a href=\"#/G5346 - φημί - phēmí - fay-mee'/5346\">G5346</a> generally refer to an <i>individual</i> expression or speech respectively; while <a href=\"#/G4483 - ῥέω - rhéō - hreh'-o/4483\">G4483</a> is properly to <i>break silence</i> merely, and <a href=\"#/G2980 - λαλέω - laléō - lal-eh'-o/2980\">G2980</a> means an <i>extended</i> or random harangue]); by implication to <i>mean:</i> - ask, bid, boast, call, describe, give out, name, put forth, say (-ing, on), shew, speak, tell, utter."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1586 - ἐκλέγομαι - eklégomai - ek-leg'-om-ahee/1586\">G1586</a>, <a href=\"#/G1588 - ἐκλεκτός - eklektós - ek-lek-tos'/1588\">G1588</a>, <a href=\"#/G1589 - ἐκλογή - eklogḗ - ek-log-ay'/1589\">G1589</a>, <a href=\"#/G249 - ἄλογος - álogos - al'-og-os/249\">G249</a>, <a href=\"#/G2980 - λαλέω - laléō - lal-eh'-o/2980\">G2980</a>, <a href=\"#/G3004 - λέγω - légō - leg'-o/3004\">G3004</a>, <a href=\"#/G3050 - λογικός - logikós - log-ik-os'/3050\">G3050</a>, <a href=\"#/G3051 - λόγιον - lógion - log'-ee-on/3051\">G3051</a>, <a href=\"#/G3052 - λόγιος - lógios - log'-ee-os/3052\">G3052</a>, <a href=\"#/G3054 - λογομαχέω - logomachéō - log-om-akh-eh'-o/3054\">G3054</a>, <a href=\"#/G3055 - λογομαχία - logomachía - log-om-akh-ee'-ah/3055\">G3055</a>, <a href=\"#/G3056 - λόγος - lógos - log'-os/3056\">G3056</a>"}]}